{"tid":1644176,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【twitter戰線】【TweetDeck】太多tweet？入來教你點樣高效睇tweet","createTime":"2019-10-10T12:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T01:09:42.000Z","uid":280046,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"66b16388fc77041b3f9b75ca12f85dbf848b4ba0","tid":1644176,"uid":280046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"知道大家最近互科手足可能搞到成個feed都係差唔多嘅嘢。點樣有效睇tweet呢？TweetDeck係一個好好用嘅工具，好多外國journalist都會用來mon住時勢。直接google tweetdeck或者呢到 <a href=\"https://tweetdeck.twitter.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftweetdeck.twitter.com%2F&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5Q4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=34bbabdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tweetdeck.twitter.com/</a> 就用到。<br />\n點用呢？你可以見到版面上面有好多個column，全部可以自製。例如我第三個column叫hk protest，擺左我自己入嘅一個list，入面我揀左幾個我覺得特別有用嗰account，我就可以方便咁睇佢地嘅tweet。呢啲column我可以封面別類整好多個，例如「名人」、「外國」、「手足」、「文宣」、「新聞」。第四個column就可以自己set search，佢會一直stay係到幫你refresh相關字詞，你就好容易見到最近啲人tweet左乜。<br />\n大家twitter戰線加油！記住唔好只retweet，發original內容+hashtag 同回覆人地comment都好重要！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZNv0ic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZNv0ic.png&h=ab1fbf17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3fcba3396d71b9badefde986a72687ff4a319c8","tid":1644176,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d248c2feee656aec4cd03434c0b3dcec6113fa39","tid":1644176,"uid":269449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"好用, p牌推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3673e94041036ecb78e63988fdb8fcee7485b6d8","tid":1644176,"uid":280046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"p牌求推"},{"pid":"0f409c1057119def925a72b0359cffb13074c461","tid":1644176,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\